        "content": "**ALERT CATEGORIES (60 Total Rules):**\n\n**Safety (10):** Heel >22\u00b0 | Pitch >15\u00b0 | System Temp >80\u00b0C | Battery <10V | InfluxDB Down | Signal K Down | GPS Loss | Network Disconnected | Critical Sensor Failure | Hull Breach Alert\n\n**Performance (15):** VMG <1kt | Speed vs Polars >20% deviation | Sail Configuration Inefficient | Trim Not Optimal | Wave Height >4m | Current Against Course | Layline Off >10\u00b0 | Heading Drift >5\u00b0 | Acceleration Low | Deceleration Unexpected | Engine Overheat | Propeller Cavitation | Fouling Detected | Leeway High | Dead Reckoning Error\n\n**Weather/Sea (15):** Wind Shift >15\u00b0 | Wind Speed Change >5kt | Squall Detected | Pressure Drop >5hPa/hr | Temperature Drop >3\u00b0C | Swell Direction Adverse | Tide Change | Current Reversal | Wave Period <6s | Whitecap Formation | Fog Bank Approaching | Lightning Detected | Barometer Trend Negative | Humidity >90% | Dew Point Warning\n\n**Systems (10):** Battery Capacity <20% | Current Draw >100A | Charger Failure | Inverter Fault | Communication Delay >2s | GPS Dilution >10 | Compass Error >5\u00b0 | Clock Sync Lost | Storage Full | Update Available\n\n**Racing (10):** Mark Rounding <2nm | Start Line Crossing | Wrong Mark Cleared | Outside Course | Penalty Received | Time Limit Approaching | Fleet Behind >5nm | Fleet Ahead <0.2nm | Finish Zone Entered | Race Finish Button\n\n\n**NAVIGATION LINKS:**  [\ud83c\udfe0 Cockpit](d/cockpit-main) | [\ud83c\udf0a Environment](d/environment-conditions) | [\u2693 Crew](d/crew-management) | [\u26a1 Performance](d/performance-analysis) | [\ud83c\udf2a\ufe0f Wind](d/wind-current-tactical) | [\ud83c\udfc6 Competitive](d/competitive-fleet) | [\ud83d\udd0b Electrical](d/electrical-power) | [\ud83c\udfc1 Race](d/race-block-island) | [\ud83d\udd14 Alerts](d/alerts-monitoring)",
